59:01.579 --> 59:03.456
- And you got
to shake the tail.

59:03.539 --> 59:04.999
- Right, yeah.
- There you go.

59:05.083 --> 59:09.212
[laughter,
cheers, and applause]

59:25.520 --> 59:28.439
<i>[light music]</i>

59:28.523 --> 59:32.318
<i>♪ ♪</i>

59:32.402 --> 59:34.487
- Next year I'm planning
to come back

59:34.570 --> 59:36.322
and bring my wife with me.
- Oh, neat.

59:36.406 --> 59:39.659
- She might as well go to
Mrs. Claus school, too, so..,

59:39.742 --> 59:41.536
- Yeah, my wife is there now.
- Okay.

59:41.619 --> 59:45.957
[indistinct chatter, laughter]

59:46.040 --> 59:49.544
- Levi, step forward, sir.
- Thank you.

59:49.627 --> 59:51.421
- Thank you.
- Ho, ho, ho!

59:51.504 --> 59:53.631
- Ho, ho, ho!

59:53.715 --> 59:59.512
<i>♪ ♪</i>

59:59.595 --> 1:00:02.807
<i>- Here's my card.</i>
- Thank you.

1:00:02.890 --> 1:00:04.809
- I love that. Awesome.

1:00:04.892 --> 1:00:06.227
Give me a high five.

1:00:06.311 --> 1:00:08.187
This has been
a wonderful experience for me.

1:00:08.271 --> 1:00:10.398
It has been.
Thank you. Bye-bye.

1:00:10.481 --> 1:00:12.233
- Bye-bye.
Come on.

1:00:12.317 --> 1:00:14.027
<i>♪ ♪</i>

1:00:14.110 --> 1:00:16.904
- So I hope you're going away
with some good memories,

1:00:16.988 --> 1:00:18.781
lots of information.

1:00:18.865 --> 1:00:23.536
And make sure you grab
a snowball on your way out

1:00:23.619 --> 1:00:27.373
<i>and take that home</i>
<i>and put it up on your desk,</i>

1:00:27.457 --> 1:00:29.042
<i>on your bedside,</i>

1:00:29.125 --> 1:00:31.002
<i>or carry it with you</i>
<i>when you go out and do gigs</i>

1:00:31.085 --> 1:00:33.796
<i>and remember that all together</i>

1:00:33.880 --> 1:00:37.633
<i>we've really created</i>
<i>a special world here</i>

1:00:37.717 --> 1:00:41.721
<i>and a special experience...</i>

1:00:41.804 --> 1:00:44.098
<i>that hopefully</i>
<i>won't melt away.</i>

1:00:44.182 --> 1:00:51.272
<i>♪ ♪</i>

